## Problem
Discovery parse failure only logs and sets `discovering = false`. No user-visible error on the panel (“No profiles” if empty). Missing `python3`, non-executable script, or install path issues look like “no accounts.”

## Location
contents/ui/ProfileController.qml:664-674

## Suggested fix
Surface `error` / empty-state message with stderr snippet; depend on pure bash JSON emit or ship a fallback without python3.

